>The composer of the track.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para
><guilabel
>Albumartiest</guilabel
></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para
>The artist or band of the album.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para
><guilabel
>Album</guilabel
></para>
    </entry>
