<sect2 id="how-to-use-configure-shortcuts---"
><title
>How to use Configure Shortcuts...</title
> 
<para>
<screenshot>
<screeninfo
></screeninfo>
  <mediaobject>
    <imageobject>
      <imagedata fileref="amarok24_configureshortcutsdialog.png" format="PNG"/>
    </imageobject>
    <textobject>
      <phrase
></phrase>
    </textobject>
  </mediaobject>
</screenshot>
</para>
<para>
<informaltable>
  <tgroup cols="2">
  <thead>
  <row>
    <entry
>Knop</entry>
    <entry
>Beschrijving</entry>
  </row>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para
><guilabel
>Search</guilabel
></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para
>Search Actions and Shortcuts.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para
><guilabel
>Details</guilabel
></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para
>Add, remove and get more information about shortcut schemes.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para
><guilabel
>Reset to Defaults</guilabel
></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para
>Reset all custom shortcuts back to default.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para
><guilabel
>Print</guilabel
></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para
>Print the list of shortcuts.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para
><guilabel
>OK</guilabel
></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para
>Save all changes.</para>
    </entry>
  </row>
  <row>
    <entry>
    <para
><guilabel
>Annuleren</guilabel
></para>
    </entry>
    <entry>
    <para
>Close window without saving changes.</para
></entry>
  </row>
  </tbody>
  </tgroup>
</informaltable>
</para>
<para
>When you select an action, that opens a sub-window where you can choose between two radio buttons, <guilabel
>Default</guilabel
> and <guilabel
>Custom</guilabel
>. If you choose <guilabel
>Default</guilabel
> you'll use the default shortcut. If you choose <guilabel
>Custom</guilabel
> you'll configure and use your shortcut for this action. </para>
